  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968410/extras/57620cb40f089d23b8ae94723601b093.avif?t=1749913862\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><br>Ahoy! Are you ready to become the bravest pirate of the seas? In Bridges of Patience, get ready to navigate through pirate-themed parkours, testing your courage and skills to overcome the levels.<br><br><strong>Wooden Bridges</strong><br>Moving bridges, rotating wooden pieces, punching walls... Will you be able to conquer these challenges? Get set to test your bravery and abilities!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968410/extras/87fb085d6ac921ccc2db24d45e2039e4.poster.avif?t=1749913862\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968410/extras/87fb085d6ac921ccc2db24d45e2039e4.webm?t=1749913862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968410/extras/87fb085d6ac921ccc2db24d45e2039e4.mp4?t=1749913862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Rumors Beyond the Sea?</strong><br>According to some rumors, a wanted pirate has escaped to these lands. If you find him, do not forget to hand him over to the authorities. They call him MANYAK KORSAN PATATES.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968410/extras/c620471747168a2c351b392ba6188157.avif?t=1749913862\" width=616 height=353 /></span><br><br><strong>Game Mechanics</strong><br>Our game includes parkour mechanics. \"W A S D\" for run, \"Space\" for jump. It's easy. Or NOT? <br>If you finish this game, I congratulate you, but if you can't, never give up, you will become a more masterful pirate every time.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968410/extras/c75a9a9506ff77e89f3793dcdb2b8a91.poster.avif?t=1749913862\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968410/extras/c75a9a9506ff77e89f3793dcdb2b8a91.webm?t=1749913862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968410/extras/c75a9a9506ff77e89f3793dcdb2b8a91.mp4?t=1749913862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968410/extras/57620cb40f089d23b8ae94723601b093.avif?t=1749913862\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><br>Ahoy! Are you ready to become the bravest pirate of the seas? In Bridges of Patience, get ready to navigate through pirate-themed parkours, testing your courage and skills to overcome the levels.<br><br><strong>Wooden Bridges</strong><br>Moving bridges, rotating wooden pieces, punching walls... Will you be able to conquer these challenges? Get set to test your bravery and abilities!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968410/extras/87fb085d6ac921ccc2db24d45e2039e4.poster.avif?t=1749913862\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968410/extras/87fb085d6ac921ccc2db24d45e2039e4.webm?t=1749913862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968410/extras/87fb085d6ac921ccc2db24d45e2039e4.mp4?t=1749913862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Rumors Beyond the Sea?</strong><br>According to some rumors, a wanted pirate has escaped to these lands. If you find him, do not forget to hand him over to the authorities. They call him MANYAK KORSAN PATATES.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968410/extras/c620471747168a2c351b392ba6188157.avif?t=1749913862\" width=616 height=353 /></span><br><br><strong>Game Mechanics</strong><br>Our game includes parkour mechanics. \"W A S D\" for run, \"Space\" for jump. It's easy. Or NOT? <br>If you finish this game, I congratulate you, but if you can't, never give up, you will become a more masterful pirate every time.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968410/extras/c75a9a9506ff77e89f3793dcdb2b8a91.poster.avif?t=1749913862\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968410/extras/c75a9a9506ff77e89f3793dcdb2b8a91.webm?t=1749913862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968410/extras/c75a9a9506ff77e89f3793dcdb2b8a91.mp4?t=1749913862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
